  "detailed_description": "Circus Challenge combines the best parts of platformer and marble games, creating an unique experience, introducing an athmosphere of horror.<br><br>Step into a world of thrilling challenges and exciting adventures where you’ll find yourself controlling a clown balancing a ball, reminiscent of a classic marble game. Navigate through treacherous paths, moving carefully to avoid falls and obstacles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921060/extras/89aacf5a4bfbdb50f22981c0ed9006dd.poster.avif?t=1741836353\" width=540 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921060/extras/89aacf5a4bfbdb50f22981c0ed9006dd.webm?t=1741836353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921060/extras/89aacf5a4bfbdb50f22981c0ed9006dd.mp4?t=1741836353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But that's not all! This is not just a marble game so you must use your feet to climb up to the peak.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921060/extras/5bd072e93fb9d1a56cf742ba827c1974.poster.avif?t=1741836353\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921060/extras/5bd072e93fb9d1a56cf742ba827c1974.webm?t=1741836353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921060/extras/5bd072e93fb9d1a56cf742ba827c1974.mp4?t=1741836353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are no second chances here - one wrong move, and you’ll have to start over. The permadeath system adds an exhilarating layer of tension and makes every decision matter.<br><br>So, are you ready to take on the challenge?<br><br>Features<br><br>    Leaderboad<br>    Achievements",
